Description: An input-output interface for reading in and writing out tractogram
    in different common formats. This data comes in the form of 3D polygons with
    possibly attributes at each point. These are obtained via tracking algorithms
    from diffusion MRI and are a non-invasive way of studying brain structural
    connectivity.
